'''Uccen''' d yiwwen uɣeṛsiw azagir yettidiren deg [[Tafriqt|Tefriqt]] akkʷed [[Asya]], yettidir daɣen deg tmura n [[Turuft]] (Uṛup) i d-yezgan ɣer tama n yilel agrakal.<br>

Uccanen ttidiren d tiwaculin, tawacult tebna ɣef imarawen akkʷed warraw (tarwa-nsen). Yal tawacult tesɛa aḥric n tmurt, tessenqad-it daɣen tettɛassa-t. Učči-nsen d amurḍus, igumma (fruits) neɣ ayen ara d-gemren, am iɣeṛsiwen imsuttaḍen imecṭaḥ, ibaɛac, igwra akkʷed igʷdaḍ (oiseaux).<br>

Uccen itteffeɣ tikkwal ad yegmer iman-is ladɣa mi ara tili tewtemt-is terfed (s tadist), tikkwal-nniḍen ttefɣen deg sin neɣ gellun ula d arraw-nsen.<br>
 
Uccen izemmel tiḥeṛci akkʷed tigzi deg yidelsan iɣeṛfanen.

